tre, balancier dot\u00e9 d\u0027un ressort-spiral-r\u00e9glant. Mouvement muni d\u0027un r\u00e9veil ; le barillet du train de sonnerie reperc\u00e9 de rinceaux. Coq circulaire \u00e0 deux pieds et les quatre piliers grav\u00e9s et ajour\u00e9s de rinceaux.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Johannes van Ceulen Haghe","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"10,2","displayDimension":"10,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"7,5","displayDimension":"7,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"La Haye (Europe-\u003EPays-Bas = Pays Bas = Hollande)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 748 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Olivier, Marie-Julie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"Olivier, Jules-Ren\u00e9","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"24\/01\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"05\/02\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"04\/08\/1935","startYear":1935,"endYear":1935}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes"